curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/collections?project\[\]=ESI&project\[\]=EVI&project\[\]=EPI"
Find collections that match all of the 'project' param values
curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/collections?project\[\]=ESI&project\[\]=EVI&project\[\]=EPI&options\[project\]\[and\]=true"
