Find granules by concept id
Note: more than one may be supplied
Find granule by concept id
curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/granules?provider=PROV1&concept_id\[\]=G1000000002-CMR_PROV1"
Find granule by echo granule id
curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/granules?provider=PROV1&echo_granule_id\[\]=G1000000002-CMR_PROV1"
Find granules by parent concept id. concept_id or collection_concept_id can be used interchangeably.
curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/granules?concept_id=C1234567-PODAAC"
curl "https://cmr.earthdata.nasa.gov/search/granules?collection_concept_id=C1234567-PODAAC"
